    %section.slide
      %h2 Who's Responsible
      %ul
        %li.slide Original implementation created by Hampton Catlin (also responsible for Sass)
        %li.slide Current implementation and maintenance by Nathan Weizenbaum
        %li.slide MIT license, source (and ability to contribute) at <a href="https://github.com/nex3/haml">https://github.com/nex3/haml</a>
        %li.slide Originally packaged with Sass
        
    %section.slide
      %blockquote
        cleaner and DRY-er<br />
        write HTML haiku<br />
        templating fun. Scraunched.
